e brightest knots are flat, indicating that the bulk of the luminosity of the\njets is emitted at GeV energies, and raising the interesting possibility of\nfuture detections with GLAST.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Jan 2004 19:50:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 28 Jan 2004 20:34:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
