e increase in X-ray flux. The fractional change in\nfrequency of 3.7x10^-5 during this event is significantly larger than the\nvalues observed in the glitches in radio pulsars and anomalous X-ray pulsars.\nWe discuss other similarities and differences between these events.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Jan 2004 21:01:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 11 Jun 2004 16:24:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
