 in this paper exploits the flatness of the\ntarget space in several important ways. In a companion paper we treat the more\ncomplicated case of curved target spaces.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Jan 2004 14:55:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-26"}
